==Geode Minerals==
Geode minerals are extracted from geodes. They are mainly used as donations to the [[Museum]], or sold for a small profit. They can be used to [[Tailoring|tailor]] or [[Dyeing|dye]] clothing.  They are generally [[Friendship#Universal Dislikes|disliked as gifts]]. [[Wizard|The Wizard]] likes all Geode Minerals.
